🌱 **Plant Watering Reminders**

🚨 **URGENT - Overdue:**
💎🌿 *Jade Plant (Office)* (Office Desk)
   💡 Water deeply but infrequently. Allow soil to dry completely between waterings.
🐍🌿 *Snake Plant (Bedroom)* (Bedroom Corner)
   💡 Very drought tolerant. Water sparingly and avoid overwatering.
🍃✨ *Golden Pothos (Kitchen)* (Kitchen Hanging Basket)
   💡 Keep soil consistently moist but not waterlogged. Loves humidity.
☮️🌸 *Peace Lily (Bathroom)* (Bathroom Shelf)
   💡 Prefers consistently moist soil. Leaves will droop when thirsty.

📅 **Due Today:**
🕷️🌱 *Spider Plant (Living Room)* (Living Room Window)
   💡 Water when top inch of soil is dry. Prefers bright, indirect light.

🌍 Current Season: 🌸 Spring

💡 **Tip of the day:** 🌡️ Room temperature water is best
